	  in CMake, not in C++

2009-09-11 17:42  harryvanderwolf

	* src/hugin1/hugin/CPDetectorConfig.cpp: [OSX] MacOSX bundle use
	  AutoCustome CP value which was therefore also used (hidden) for
	  other OSses. I disabled this functionality (not removed) due to
	  the fact that MacOSX now adopted TModes AutoCP generator
	  structure. This needs to be dealt with carefully for the 2009.4
	  release

2009-09-11 17:42  harryvanderwolf

	* src/hugin1/hugin/CPDetectorConfig_default.h: [OSX] MacOSX bundle
	  comes without default AutoCP generator since mid 2008 as we want
	  to prevent any patent conflicts

