2008-08-31 09:14  harryvanderwolf

	* CMakeModules/FindSubversion.cmake: [Mac] modify
	  FindSubversion.cmake. Stupid Leopard comes with a way too old
	  subversion and cmake defaults to Leopard one. Needs binary
	  subversion from http://homepage.mac.com/martinott/ or build with
	  MacPorts or Fink

