	  src/hugin1/hugin/huginApp.cpp,
	  src/hugin1/hugin/xrc/images_panel.xrc,
	  src/hugin1/hugin/xrc/main_frame.xrc: Custom XRC handlers for
	  Images, Photometric, and Pano panels. Removed user dragable
	  splitters from Images and Lens panel. Should fix some long
	  standing layout issues. Scrollbars in Images and Lens panels are
	  currently broken.

