2007-11-01 00:03  dangelo

	* src/hugin1/hugin/AutoCtrlPointCreator.cpp,
	  src/hugin1/stitch_project/hugin_stitch_project.cpp: fixed error
	  when running autopano kolor

2007-11-01 00:02  dangelo

	* src/hugin1/base_wx/MyExternalCmdExecDialog.cpp,
	  src/hugin1/base_wx/MyExternalCmdExecDialog.h: wxProcess does not
	  work in wxMSW as it works on Mac and Unix.
	  Output of the child process can't be captured, trying to use
	  a standard windows console to execute, but make.exe executes
	  without console, while autopano does.

2007-10-30 23:15  dangelo

	* src/hugin1/base_wx/MyExternalCmdExecDialog.cpp: Use
	  wxInputStream::CanRead() instead of wxProcess::IsInputAvailable()
	  to check for output
	  from the child process. IsInputAvailable() uses polling and
	  consumes as much CPU as it can get.
	  Autopano run from within hugin should be twice as fast now.
	  Disabled running the programs in an external xterm.

2007-10-29 22:37  dangelo

	* src/hugin1/stitch_project/hugin_stitch_project.cpp: Add directory
	  of hugin_stitch_project exectuable to path, required
	  for finding the other binaries such as make etc.

