2006-12-18 20:33  dangelo

	* src/Panorama/PTOptimise.cpp, src/Panorama/Panorama.cpp,
	  src/hugin/AssistantPanel.cpp, src/include/PT/PTOptimise.h,
	  src/include/PT/PanoCommand.h, src/include/PT/Panorama.h: Better
	  heuristics for "Align" function. Now optimizes a,b,c if the
	  control points are distributed well. Also optimizes FOV for 360
	  degree panoramas, or heavily overlapping images.

