2006-08-17 19:58  ippei

	* src/include/hugin/config_defaults.h: Default back to PTStitcher
	  on OSX. The previous change breaks the compatibility with 0.6
	  users. They probably have the default value "PTStitcher" in their
	  preference, which would be considered 'custom' if we changed the
	  default value now.

