2006-06-08 21:59  dangelo

	* configure.ac: previous change always disabled hugin and nona_gui

2006-06-08 20:15  dangelo

	* configure.ac, src/Makefile.am: added --disable-gui configure
	  option, for people that just want to build
	  fulla and nona. This does not require wxWidgets.

2006-06-08 06:08  dangelo

	* src/tools/fulla.cpp: bugfix: gamma setting doesn't enforce PTLens
	  lookup

2006-06-07 06:12  dangelo

	* src/Panorama/SpaceTransform.cpp, src/include/PT/SpaceTransform.h,
	  src/tools/fulla.cpp: fulla: minor speedup by incoporating scaling
	  into first distortion
	  correction.

2006-06-04 23:17  dangelo

	* src/tools/fulla.cpp, src/tools/fulla.vcproj: fulla: fixed radial
	  vignetting correction, added gamma option

2006-06-04 21:48  dangelo

	* src/Panorama/SpaceTransform.cpp, src/build_msvc/Hugin.sln,
	  src/hugin/hugin.vcproj, src/include/PT/SpaceTransform.h,
	  src/tools/fulla.cpp, src/tools/fulla.vcproj: fulla:
	  * improved merging of green and (red,blue) correction
	  coefficients.
	  The previous scheme was an approximation and could lead to
	  errors of 0.2 pixels in a 6 megapixel image.
	  * added option to output unscaled output with black borders.

2006-06-04 12:51  dangelo

	* src/include/PT/SpaceTransform.h, src/tools/fulla.cpp: fixed
	  serious bug in fulla that lead to wrong tca correction
	  coefficients being used. Now TCA & distortion correction should
	  work at the same time.

