2005-08-10 22:05  dangelo

	* src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp, src/hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp,
	  src/hugin/ImagesPanel.cpp, src/hugin/LensPanel.cpp,
	  src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp, src/hugin/OptimizePanel.cpp,
	  src/hugin/huginApp.cpp, src/hugin/po/de.po, src/hugin/po/fr.po,
	  src/hugin/po/hugin.pot, src/hugin/po/it.po, src/hugin/po/ja.po,
	  src/hugin/po/pl.po, src/hugin/po/ru.po,
	  src/include/hugin/CPEditorPanel.h,
	  src/include/hugin/ImagesPanel.h, src/include/hugin/LensPanel.h,
	  src/include/hugin/MainFrame.h: work around some changed behaviour
	  and bugs in wxWidgets 2.6.1 on unix (wxgtk).
	  Splitters are restored to their original size and 'f' key
	  finetunes on the
	  image with the mouse cursor over it.
	  
	  also updated translations.

