2005-05-19 20:32  dangelo

	* src/hugin/PreviewFrame.cpp, src/hugin/PreviewPanel.cpp,
	  src/include/hugin/PreviewPanel.h: do not update when preview
	  window is minimized. Unfortunately, we can't
	  be notified when the preview window is un-minimized. Therefore we
	  cannot update
	  the preview then, even if it is desired by the auto-update.
	  Workaround: removed
	  minimize box from Preview Frame

