2005-01-17 01:29  dangelo

	* src/Panorama/PanoToolsInterface.cpp, src/Panorama/Panorama.cpp,
	  src/Panorama/PanoramaMemento.cpp,
	  src/Panorama/SpaceTransform.cpp, src/common/utils.cpp,
	  src/hugin/CPZoomDisplayPanel.cpp,
	  src/hugin/ImageOrientationPanel.cpp, src/hugin/ImagesList.cpp,
	  src/hugin/LensPanel.cpp, src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp,
	  src/include/PT/Panorama.h, src/include/PT/PanoramaMemento.h,
	  src/include/PT/SpaceTransform.h, src/include/common/utils.h,
	  src/include/hugin/LensPanel.h, src/include/hugin/wxPanoCommand.h:
	  Better EXIF reading:
	  1. handle cases where focal length and equiv. focal length are
	  given
	  but not the sensor size.
	  2. Ask if for crop factor if it is needed, but not in exif data.
	  3. redone hfov <-> focal length calculations, support rectilinear
	  and fisheye
	  lenses.

