2004-10-29 16:56  dangelo

	* src/hugin/ImageCache.cpp: support 8, 16, 32, float, double images
	  inside hugin. Accept Gray and RGB image with or without alpha
	  channel. Images are converted to 8 bit during loading.
	  The 8 bit images are only used for the preview images inside
	  hugin.

