2004-09-08 21:56  dangelo

	* src/hugin/PanoPanel.cpp: removed stupid cut'n'paste error that
	  created the nona output files before the stitching.
	  This broke nona stitching if the correct file extension was
	  specified.

2004-09-08 21:54  dangelo

	* src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp, src/hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp,
	  src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp, src/include/hugin/CPEditorPanel.h,
	  src/include/hugin/CPImageCtrl.h, src/include/panoinc_WX.h,
	  src/include/vigra_ext/Correlation.h: added new correlation
	  function that will also search for rotated patches.
	  it must be enabled in the config file (or registry), by setting
	  CPEditorPanel/RotationSearch = 1
	  the angle interval that should be tried can be specified with
	  
	  CPEditorPanel/RotationStartAngle
	  CPEditorPanel/RotationStopAngle
	  CPEditorPanel/RotationSteps

2004-09-08 21:23  dangelo

	* src/Panorama/Panorama.cpp: fixed control point parsing bug with
	  newer pano12.dll's

2004-09-08 21:22  dangelo

	* src/common/utils.cpp: fixed error when the path to an output file
	  contained a .

2004-08-30 22:58  dangelo

	* src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp: fix endless loop on removing images,
	  looks like an unsigned int can get
	  negative with the gcc 3.3 under linux, that is (! (uint >= 0))
	  can become
	  true..

2004-08-30 07:38  dangelo

	* src/hugin/LensPanel.cpp: fixed a typo (file dialog was called
	  save instead of load)

